productDes: The modern crystal table lamp features a stunning 3D rose design made from high-quality acrylic. With 16 color-changing options and remote or touch control, it sets the perfect ambiance. Dimmable with four modes, it’s an exquisite gift for any occasion.

This is a Portable Power bank with many features. It also holds an extendable table lamp with a long & flexible neck. There are 3 simple gears to adjust the light levels from bright to the brightest. A great desk accessory and gift to give to your employees.

Illuminate your space with this Crystal Lamp, featuring a mesmerizing rose crystal diamond design that adds a touch of glamour and sophistication to any room. With Wireless Touch Control & Remote Magic, this light comes in 16 different colours.

This electric coffee mug is designed to keep your beverage at constant temperature throughout the day, helping you have warm, delicious tea/coffee/soup anytime & anywhere. Made of water-proof tempered glass, the warmer area is 3.5 in diameter.
productImage: This versatile lamp features a 360° magnetic design with three magnetic balls for easy angle adjustments. Use it as a desk lamp, flashlight, or bedside light. With USB-C charging, touch control, and three brightness levels, it's perfect for reading, camping, or emergencies. Durable and elegant design
